{
  "stem": "4187.2",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And there was a-- there was a window, a small window, but it wasn't open.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It had wire across it.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So it was, you know, wired up, heavily wired up.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So you got a little bit of lighting and a little bit of airing, but only just enough not to suffocate.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So can you imagine 70 people-- and naturally, we had nothing to eat, not a thing to eat, right through the three days.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "That's July the fourth that we were put into-- into the wagons, into the cattle train.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And we arrived on the seventh.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And in that time, we had no food.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Now, there were a number of old people there, naturally, quite old people.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And-- and there were-- there were, at least I would say, three deaths in-- in the-- in the train, because the heat was just so incredible, you know?",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "People just couldn't-- couldn't stand up to it.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And the wailing was unbelievable.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And my-- my young sister was, of course, next to my mother.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And I-- I-- I remember her saying to my mother, you won't let them separate me from you, will you?",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And, of course, my mother kept saying, never.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "No, never.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "Never.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "She must have somehow felt something.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And we-- my-- my other sister-- well, actually, my little sister as well-- we actually stood up to the strain, comparatively speaking, pretty well.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But we were terrified, absolutely terrified.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We weren't getting sick.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We didn't faint.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "There was no-- there wasn't anything that I can say to you, this and this happened.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "It didn't.",
      "word_count": 2
    }
  ],
